snippet.title: SL Equity Guide
snippet.description:
SL Equity Guide is an educative channel on investment opportunities of equities/stocks listed in Sri Lanka's Colombo Stock Exchange (CSE). This channel contains video materials on Sri Lanka stock market performance, analysis of listed stocks/securities, stock valuations and future prospects, fundamental analysis as well as technical analysis on company performances and stock price movements, earnings updates of stocks (quarterly as well as annual), industry/sector analysis and many more. 

We focuses on value investing mainly based on fundamental analysis and show the potential investors about the undervalued stocks in the market based on the intrinsic value principle. Our strategy works best for investors who are patient as well as ready to invest and hold the stock for a longer time, at least two to three quarters.

snippet.title: PassengerParamvir Shorts
snippet.description:
Namaste, I'm Paramvir Singh Beniwal, a 25 year old lad with an ambition to travel the world! I'm passionate about exploring new cultures, meeting new people & learning new languages. I graduated from Hindu College - Delhi University (Zoology Hons.) in 2018 and I've mostly been travelling since then (although my first International trip was to USA back in 2015). I'm a former Volleyball player and I love lifting weights too! 
I've travelled across 28 countries and have also been to places which are considered to be the riskiest by many, including Syria, Somalia, Omo valley, Lebanon,  etc.

snippet.title: Lehmann Vlogs
snippet.description:
TRAVEL WITH US TO NEW PLACES!

We are Mark and Lara with polish and german roots, traveling the world together since 2017. One day, Mark grabbed the camera and started documenting our travel adventures. Now we are more than happy to look back on so many collected memories, people that we met through youtube, and adventures we captured on camera. In 2020 we decided to leave Germany to fulfill our passion. We left home with 2 carry-on bags in a worldwide pandemic in June 2021 and can't imagine stopping traveling the world anytime soon! Thank you for following our journey!

snippet.title: Dr. Noel Knows
snippet.description:
Dr Noel Somasundaram is Consultant Endocrinologist, Diabetes and Hormone Centre, Colombo, Sri Lanka. He is the President of South Asian Federation of Endocrine Societies and Project Lead for Sri Lanka Diabetes and Cardiovascular Initiative a national project for prevention and control of non-communicable diseases. 

Dr Noel Somasundaram has more than 100 publications in the field of diabetes, endocrinology and metabolism. He is the editor of Clinical Diabetology and has chapters in fifteen textbooks including Oxford Desktop Reference in Endocrinology and International Textbook for Diabetes. He has been Principal investigator in many international studies.

He was former Consultant Endocrinologist at National Hospital of Sri Lanka.  His pioneering work includes introduction of comprehensive care for patients with diabetes, obesity, pituitary tumours and craniopharyngioma, introduction of hormone testing and catheter studies for complex endocrine disorders to Sri Lanka.

snippet.title: Blissful Mind
snippet.description:
Welcome to Blissful Mind your space for calm and self-care. We are a team of professionals in mental healthcare and therapy who ourselves have won our battles against stress, anxiety, and panic and in turn, have helped hundreds of people overcome their struggles with our simple mindful techniques. We are creating this online sanctuary to share tips, guidelines, and brief sessions that could help you maintain your mental wellbeing, manage your stress and relax. This space is for you, for your mind, for you to learn to care more for yourself and to help you live a better, healthier life.
 
 
DISCLAIMER 
The content shared in this space are offered solely as guidelines. These should not be considered as an alternative for seeking the help of a mental healthcare professional if the need be, who could diagnose and determine the best course of treatment for you.

snippet.title: Barberyn Ayurveda Resorts
snippet.description:
Barberyn, the pioneer of Ayurveda Resorts, opened the first fully dedicated Ayurvedic resort in the world in 1984. Today, Barberyn offers travelers in search of natural healing a choice of two resorts: 
- Barberyn Reef Ayurveda Resort, in Beruwala, Sri Lanka - the classic hotel on the beach. Heal your body, mind and spirit in the holistic experience of Ayurveda. 
- Barberyn Beach Ayurveda Resort, in Weligama, Sri Lanka - experience authentic Ayurveda and Yoga in a luxurious beach holiday with a breathtaking view of the Indian Ocean. 

In addition, there is Diyabubula, the Barberyn Art & Jungle Hideaway, a small luxury hotel in Central Sri Lanka, close to the most interesting cultural sites of Sri Lanka, but also near to spectacular national parks. Enjoy a few days in this unique resort with its creator, renowned Sri Lankan artist Laki Senanayake.

snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel, Azi's Kitchen & Garden!

I just love food but cooking was a stressful task and a major obstacle to me, since I had no hands on experience.  My lack of creativity made me believe I was hopeless. But I was so  inspired to overcome this obstacle because of my kids. Their compliments and motivation each time I prepared a meal made me believe in miracles. Therefore I challenged myself and took upon the task of traversing through baking and cooking. Improving along the way, I am just loving it. Better late than never!

I stumbled upon gardening by accident. I have loved greenery from childhood. Especially fruit trees and vegetable gardening more than flora. My new hobby gives me immense self satisfaction and self sufficiency.

Be it patchwork, fabric painting, embroidery, paper quilling, greeting card making or origami,  experimenting and creating craft is another hobby which I do to calm my senses and boost my self esteem. 

Hope you enjoy my videos!

en_GB.title: Higher Education Srilanka
en_GB.description:
Dr. Duleen Dharmaratne started his Social Educational charity of providing FREE education to the school children of Sri Lanka back in April, 2021. Currently the charity provides FREE education for more than 700 children all around the country.

" ‡∂¢‡∂∫‡∑Ä‡∑í‡∂¢‡∂∫ - ‡∑É‡∑í‡∑É‡∑î‡∑É‡∑Ä‡∑í‡∂∫ " is the name of this charity project under Higher Education Sri Lanka.  This project is carried through out the country via district leaders from 10 separate districts.
Weekly they organize Free Science seminars for O/L & A/L students as well as Motivational programmes and Online Study Sessions. Free Student consultation programmes are conducted to guide students in their own career pathways. 

If you wish to join this charity programme,

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Beyond Boundaries with Sayul
snippet.description:
How I Let Go of My Expectations and Learned Unconditional Love...

He was perfect.  
My expectations already had his life all planned out for him.
He will crawl and one day even walk. 
He will say Mom.
He will go to school. 
He will be smart. 
He will play sports. 
He will be brave. 
He will get married and have babies.
I had great expectations. 

And then right before his third birthday, I heard the words, ‚ÄúYour son fits the diagnostic criteria for autism‚Äù.
In an instant, my boy‚Äôs life vanished right before me.

But now I remind myself how awful it would feel if someone constantly expected me to be different and to be someone I‚Äôm not.

I‚Äôve learned the very definition of unconditional love is choosing to love someone exactly for who they are.
A love not based on expectations, but on reality.
I‚Äôve finally knocked down that brick house of expectations. 
Turns out it was hiding the most incredible view.

(Chrissy Kelly who has two sons on the autism spectrum)

snippet.title: Beauty of Sri Lanka (BoS)üèï
snippet.description: Sri Lanka is one of the most popular tourist destinations because it contains a mixture of unique wild life, golden beaches, a rich cultural heritage and amazing landscapes. Thousands of tourists visit Sri Lanka annually.There are many wildlife parks such as Yala,Wilpattu and Kumana. Tourists like to watch wild animals wandering in their natural surroundings.The sandy beach is also another attraction, Sri Lanka has. Many tourists spend their holidays swimming, diving and sailing here.Sri Lanka has a heritage of over 2,500 years. Ancient ruins can be seen in Anuradhapura,Polonnaruwa,Sigiriya and Yapahuwa. Tourists stop over to see wonderful creations, paintings and ruins of great buildings and monuments.There are attractive waterfalls in Sri Lanka such as Dunhinda,Diyaluma and Bambarakanda. Dunhinda is the most beautiful, while Bambarakanda is the tallest waterfall.  More tourists come to Sri Lanka to visit these attractive places.So, we can be proud of the beauty of our country.

snippet.title: sadu Education
snippet.description:
Sadu education, initiated by Mr. saman kumara de silva who is a pioneer in teaching health and physical education in many government schools of sri Lanka. Presently he is the teacher at karakkuwa sugathananda national school.

The main goal of this channel is to give free education for students from grade 06 -grade 11. This channel mainly focusses on teaching health and physical education in Sinhala medium under the curriculum given by ministry of education in Sri Lanka. The channel also provides students free education to learn Sinhala and geography.

At the first stage PowerPoint presentations are used and in second step tutor is explaining the power point presentation in order to give students a research based education.

Vision:-Every student deserve access to free education
Mission:-Enhancing students educational skills to face the competitive society

To be the most recognized qualification for middle-level accounting professionals.

Mission
To provide our students a route to success in life by helping them become competent middle-level accountants who add value to their employers. We provide our members an opportunity for career progression and networking, our staff an empowered and enjoyable working environment, and education service providers an opportunity to develop their delivery competency while co-operating for mutual gain with accounting & academic institutions.

In addition, the free online education platform, DP IELTS, supports future leaders of Sri Lanka by providing access to all video learning materials for their study abroad and global job opportunities. Furthermore, for the first time in Sri Lanka, all learners of DP IELTS can test their knowledge with Artificial Intelligence-assisted IELTS mock-up testing on the DP IELTS website for free. This is the newest addition of the Dhammika & Pricilla Perera Foundation in providing a free, world-class education for everyone. 
 
All you need for IELTS success ‚Äì DP IELTS

snippet.title: Uni Life

Yes, many people hear that he gave a lower result than us and now he is doing a good degree, that his degree has better jobs than the degree we are doing, so bring a little solution to those problems, bring details about those degree courses This is how this channel is created, many people want to do a job abroad. Having a degree is a good reason to apply for a job in a highly developed country. So put in a little effort and get a degree on a government campus. It will make it so much easier to go about your dreams. Remember learning is a thorn in the side, the fruit is a flower, and the path to success has not been paved with roses. Work hard and learn something well.
